<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٤٣٧ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا صَدَقَةُ بْنُ الْفَضْلِ:</span> أَخْبَرَنَا ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ، عَنْ ابْنِ أَبِي نَجِيحٍ، عَنْ مُجَاهِدٍ، عَنْ أَبِي مَعْمَرٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ مَسْعُودٍ <span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>انْشَقَّ الْقَمَرُ عَلَى عَهْدِ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١٣٣١⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>شِقَّتَيْنِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(اشْهَدُوا)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٣٦٥٦، ٣٦٥٨، ٤٥٨٣، ٤٥٨٤]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
